Player_ch: “Sadie, I found your tissues.”

Sadie: (Speaks incoherently.)

Sadie: “Thank you, kind stranger. I've been stuck crying for days, but thanks to you, I can finally do the thing I love most—talk.”

Player_ch: “Look! I have my body back!”

Sadie: “That is amazing! But your journey is nearing its end. There is one more puzzle awaiting you beyond these trees. Remember, if you need anything, don't hesitate to ask me.”